### 1. 📊 Dashboard

**Purpose**: The opening impression. Shows why this is an AI product, not a BI tool.

**Layout** (grid):
```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│  Period: [ April 2026 ] [ May 2026 ] [▶ Compare ]  │
├──────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│ ── COMPUTED METRICS ──────────────────────────────── │
│  CSAT 38.78%  │ Avg 3.02/5 │ 60k responses │ -20pp  │
├──────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│ ── AI-DERIVED INSIGHTS ──────────────────────────────│
│  Business Health Score: 31/100 [animated ring]      │
│  Operational Priority: APP RELIABILITY               │
│  Highest Risk Area: App (36.2% of complaints)        │
│  Fastest Growing Issue: Price (+20.3pp MoM)          │
│  Bright Spot: Staff (highest rated theme)            │
├──────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│ ── AI EXECUTIVE BRIEF ───────────────────────────────│
│  [Real Groq-generated 3-sentence paragraph]          │
│  "GreenLeaf Bistro is experiencing a critical..."    │
│  [Regenerate] [Copy]                                │
├──────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│ ── AI INSIGHTS FEED ─────────────────────────────────│
│  ⚠️  App complaints are 2.3× higher than wait_time   │
│  ↑   Price dissatisfaction grew +20.3pp MoM          │
│  ✓   Staff ratings are the only positive signal      │
│  📌  59% CSAT target gap: 20.22pp deficit            │
└──────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

**Why this works in demo**: Opens with data + AI insight in the same view. The "Business Health Score" and Executive Brief are Groq-generated on page load — it is visibly AI, not hardcoded.

**Honest complexity**:
- Business Health Score = weighted formula (`csat×0.4 + avg_rating/5×0.3 + theme_severity×0.3`) — computed, not AI
- AI insights = one Groq call that returns a JSON list of insight strings
- Executive Brief = one Groq call, cached 60 seconds

**Backend needed**: `GET /api/dashboard?period=may` (no LLM for KPIs, one LLM call for brief + insights)

**Complexity**: Medium | **Demo Value**: Very High ✅ **Build**

